	   <tr><td colspan=2>You need to look at things from a different direction.&nbsp;&nbsp;You are way too into stats.  Other from strength and stamina , i really dont see any use in dexterity and agility , i find them worthless.  What IS important is AC/RESISTS.  I cant tell you how many times i see twinks that are stat junkies.  My advice<br><br>Head - crown of froglock kings (costs about 1k-1500 might be hard since alot of peeps want this item)<br>Ears - Orc fang earings (it gives ac/hp/str hard to beet)<br>Face - sarnak hide mask/golden diamond mask(sarnak mask is about 2k, golden diamond mask is enchanter made and is about 1500 , no ac on the goldend diamond mask but the resists it gives are well worth it.)<br>Neck - lava pendant/chiped velium amulet (pendant is a few thousand , amulet is a few hundred)<br>Shoulders - drolvarg mantle (about 100)<br>Fingers - Velium fire weding rings/jagged bands(jagged bands are about 20-50pp , velium fire are about 400-600)<br>Wrists - hardend clay bracelet/granite bracers/symbol of loyalty to vox/ (hardened clay is about 3k , duno about granite / symbol of loyalty to vox is about 50-100pp.<br>Arms - azure sleeves (about 600-1k)<br>Chest - Formans tunic / crystal covered shroud / cured silk tizmak tunic (formans is cheap , 100pp maybe , shroud is about 500 , and cured tizmak is cheap but im not sure the price , i would use the cured tizmak tunic if you can handle the slightly high weight.<br>Back - white wolfhide cloak/spider fur cloak (white wolfhide is about 700-1k , spider fur is about 3-4k although price is droping.)<br>Feet - cured silk/cresent (there are a few alternatives but are quite expensive.)<br>Legs - gatorscale/wu's/drakel wolfhide legs(gator is about 500?/drakel wolfhide legings are nice but are a tad rare.)<br>Waist - fbss/tbb/thick leather apron(fbss if you have the cash , tbb if you have the cash , thick leather apron if you DONT have the cash =D ).<br>Hands - gem inlaid gauntlents/treants fist(gem inlaid gloves are about 100-200 , treant fists are a long quest that isnt really worth it.)<br><br>Thats about it , maybe you can find beter.  However i have to stress again , AC/RESISTS is MUCH more important than stats !!!<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Corr<br>60 Grandmaster of the celestial fists<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=31645" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=31645</a><br></td></tr>
