	   <tr><td colspan=2>Off-hand damage goes strictly by damage output formula (no dam bonus):&nbsp;&nbsp;(damage*2+1)/delay.  Not figuring in the proc, the KD well out-damages the yak club - by 20% or so.  The question is how often will club proc?  You have a great dex, but you'll be using weapon off-hand.  Procs once per mob?  Once every 2 mobs?  I personally wouldn't go that way, but it's a tough call.<br><br>Keyeluke <br>Monk of the Silent Fist, 50th Circle <br>Strange Brew <br>Druzzil Ro <br>&nbsp;<br>Keyeluke<br>Member of Tenacity - Druzzil Ro<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415</a></td></tr>
