	   <tr><td colspan=2>No rent items are usually summoned items (usually from magicians.) They include anything from summoned bread and water, summoned shurikens (that's a spell a monk could use...) summoned lightstones, coldstones, heatstones, etc..<br><br>What it means is that it's only a temporary item. When you log off, it'll be gone forever, and you won't have it the next time you log back on. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
