	   <a name=99606480446691></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99606480446691><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=3&mid=99606480446691>RE: A few questions</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=3&mid=99606480446691#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=57570><span id=Guru>Niteklaw</span></a>, <span id=Guru>Guru</span><br><span id=notbold>314 posts</td></tr>
