	   <tr><td colspan=2>As you get better special attacks, you can just forget about the older ones, and stick exclusively to the new ones.&nbsp;&nbsp;Eventually, flying kick will be your bread-and-butter special attack.  One note, though - Dragon Punch and Eagle Strike are used at levels 59-60 with a couple monk disciplines.  So, eventually you'll want to work on maxing those out.  Don't worry that yet though - you've got some hunting to do first.<br><br>You don't need to have all your skills max max maxed every level - just keep them close.  When u can afford 80-100 pp get a bamboo bo stick for 2hb.  It weighs 1.0 and is fast - so you'll practice your skill up faster.<br><br>Keyeluke <br>Monk of the Silent Fist, 50th Circle <br>Strange Brew <br>Druzzil Ro<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Keyeluke<br>Member of Tenacity - Druzzil Ro<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415</a></td></tr>
