	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f9959120611210><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=3&mid=9959120611210>RE: Headbands and Sashes</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=3&mid=9959120611210#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=35651><span id=Guru>Keyeluke</span></a>, <span id=Guru>Guru</span><br><span id=notbold>668 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Jul 23rd 2:14 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.86]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>The headband and sash quests are part of the Epic Quest for monks - you eventually need the red sash and the purple headband.&nbsp;&nbsp;Each headband/sash is needed for the next one - white, yellow, orange, red, purple.  The nice thing about the Monk epic is that it starts at lvl 1, and you can get experience working on your epic throughout your career.  You have the white sash - that implies you're a Freeport monk.  You'll have to get your faction up a bit in Qeynos to do the sashes there.  At your level, you can go into Blackburrow and kill gnolls to your heart's content to build faction, plus you need drops there for one of the headbands.<br><br>Shen and Dareb are for red headband - hold onto them for dear life - they're hard to find.  <br><br>Allakhazam has all the info you need on the quests.<br><br>To answer your question, I'd suggest you get to doing your sashes and headbands as soon as possible - if you wait till later, you'll do everything easily, but you'll get no experience while doing them, and I'd consider that a bit inefficient.<br><br>Keyeluke <br>Monk of the Silent Fist, 49th Circle <br>Strange Brew <br>Druzzil Ro<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Keyeluke<br>Member of Tenacity - Druzzil Ro<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415</a></td></tr>
